    <Title><![CDATA[Interesting build targets]]></Title>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[bindist]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>The target builds the <code>.zip</code>-archive as it is downloaded when getting the OpenCms release for installation.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[updater]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>The target builds the OpenCms updater.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[war]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>The target builds the <code>opencms.war</code> file as deployed to the servlet container.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[dist_{module name}]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>The target builds the <code>.zip</code> file for the respective module, as you use it for module import.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[jar_{module name}]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>The target builds the Java library (<code>.jar</code>) for the specified module.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[clean]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>The target removes all build results, i.e., cleans up.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
